{"type":"message","id":"d1dbd1bb","parentId":"200e45f5","timestamp":"2026-04-23T21:00:27.666Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:866c8532-98cb-4ec8-9501-4271382c070d maiy-draft-evening] You are master-orchestrator. Trigger article-writing agent to draft tomorrow's EVENING article.\n\nTODAY'S DATE: Use `date` command to get current date, then add 1 day.\n\nTOMORROW'S EVENING TOPIC (rotates by day):\n- Mon → CTDL: Arrays & Sorting\n- Tue → CTDL: Tree & Graph\n- Wed → C++ Thực chiến\n- Thu → JavaScript Patterns\n- Fri → Java OOP + Collections\n- Sat → DSA: Dynamic Programming\n- Sun → Python cho người mới\n\nTASK for article-writing agent:\n1. Spawn article-writing agent (runtime=subagent)\n2. Write a complete MDX article about tomorrow's programming topic\n3. Article specs:\n   - Title: compelling Vietnamese title\n   - Content: 500-800 words, MUST include code examples (C++/Java/JS/Python)\n   - Category: ctdl or web-dev\n   - Tags: 3-5 relevant tags (algorithm, cpp, java, javascript, tutorial)\n   - Excerpt: 1-2 sentences\n   - Reading time: 6-8 minutes\n   - Scheduled for: TOMORROW's date at 19:00 ICT\n4. Save MDX to: /root/.openclaw/workspaces2/v4-ecosystem-review/maiy-tech-hub/content/articles/[category]/[slug].mdx\n5. Add to queue via: POST http://localhost:3000/api/cron/publish with slot='evening', scheduledDate=TOMORROW\n6. Report completion to this session\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 23rd, 2026 - 9:00 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-23 21:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776978027629}}
