{"type":"message","id":"7f63bb13","parentId":"37ca3239","timestamp":"2026-04-23T21:00:56.455Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, now I have enough context. Let me spawn the article-writing agent with all the details.\n\nTomorrow: 2026-04-24\nTopic: Java OOP + Collections\nCategory: web-dev\nSlug: java-oop-collections-master\n\nLet me now spawn the article-writing agent with comprehensive instructions.","thinkingSignature":"efa94a7def33d211687b6b22b4156ea2932dd6ed6da5c9c0cea3b9c6edcab53c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_57rikxcga1ln_1","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"task":"You are the article-writing agent for MAIY Tech Hub. Write a complete MDX article about tomorrow's programming topic.\n\n## Context\n- Today's date: 2026-04-23\n- Tomorrow's date: 2026-04-24 (Friday)\n- Topic: **Java OOP + Collections**\n- Category: `web-dev`\n- Scheduled for: 2026-04-24 at 19:00 ICT (UTC+7)\n\n## Task\nWrite a complete, publication-ready MDX article.\n\n## Article Specifications\n\n**Title:** Something compelling in Vietnamese (e.g., \"Java OOP & Collections: Bộ Đôi Bất Khả Chiến Bại Cho Lập Trình Viên Backend\")\n\n**Frontmatter fields:**\n```yaml\ntitle: \"...\"\nslug: java-oop-collections-master\nexcerpt: \"...\"\ncontent: \"...\" (500-800 words, MUST include Java code examples)\ncategory: \"web-dev\"\ntags: [\"java\", \"oop\", \"collections\", \"tutorial\", \"backend-dev\"]\nreadingTime: \"6-8 phút\"\npublished: false\nscheduledDate: \"2026-04-24T19:00:00+07:00\"\n```\n\n**Content Requirements:**\n- Vietnamese language throughout\n- Structure: Mở đầu → Giới thiệu OOP (4 tính chất) → Collections Framework → Ví dụ code thực tế → Kết luận\n- MUST include working Java code examples showing: class definition, inheritance, interface, ArrayList, HashMap usage\n- Tone: technical but approachable, like a well-written tutorial blog\n- Practical insights, not just theory\n\n## File Output\nSave the MDX file to:\n`/root/.openclaw/